    <h1>AlphaOS Investment Research</h1>
    <p class="lead">An AI fund-research workspace designed and implemented around Jiyu Fund’s institutional-service context, connecting fund screening, research one-pagers, internal-material RAG, a multi-agent investment committee, and decision memory in one traceable workflow.</p>

