    <h2>Current Boundaries</h2>
    <p>This is a working product prototype designed around Jiyu Fund’s institutional-service context; it is not an official Jiyu Fund system. Public fund data and demonstration snapshots support research drafting only and do not constitute fund ratings, investment advice, or subscription and redemption instructions. Internal APIs, live holdings, authorization controls, and licensed databases would require formal access and compliance review.</p>

